name: Foglie #3243
description:
The Foglie series [1] consists of several pieces of generative art that display organic, leaf-like structures. The series uses the same core generating algorithm as the earlier t-SNE series [2] but renders the resulting point arrangements with filled polygons. Additionally, the color scales have been selected to produce warm, earth-like tones. Created on Oct. 13, 2021. Made in R using the {ggplot2} and {Rtsne} packages.

Sources:
[1] https://clauswilke.com/art/project/foglie
[2] https://clauswilke.com/art/project/t-sne
